This paper discusses the use of natural language processing and data mining techniques to detect and classify rumours on social media platforms. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Computation and Language (cs.CL), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
